Wordle 432 is the latest five letter word challenge that has gone live on Thursday August 25. If you're having difficulty trying to figure out the daily Wordle answer today and don't want your winning streak ruined then Express Online is here to help. We've rounded-up some hints and clues that will help you figure out the answer for Wordle 432 today. For those not in the know, Wordle is a hugely popular online word game that has taken the world by storm this past year. Each day the Wordle website is updated with a new five letter word that players have six guesses to figure out. Answers are entered into a tiled grid and there are a few pointers which help Wordle players figure out the answer. If the letter they entered is not found in the word a tile will appear grey, if it is in the word but not in the correct position it will turn yellow, while if the letter is in the word and in the correct position the tile will become green. This colour system helps Wordle players share on social media how they figured out the answer without giving any spoilers away. If someone posts one row that's all in green it shows they managed to figure out the Wordle answer in one go. What a clever clogs! If you're having trouble with the latest daily Wordle - Wordle 432 - which is out on Thursday August 25 then Express Online has rounded up some tips to help below. We've got some general Wordle tips and tricks followed by specific guidance for Wordle 432... General Wordle tips and tricks... • Don't use the same letter twice in your opening guess. • Try to use a couple of vowels in your first guess, particularly 'A' and 'E'. • Avoid letters such as 'X', 'Z' and 'Q' until later on, when you have a better idea what the answer is. • 'RAISE' is a good word to start with, while 'TOUCH' is a decent second guess. • Check out the daily hints provided by Express Online below... Wordle 432 hints and clues for August 25... 1. Wordle 432 starts with the letter C. 2. Wordle 432 contains one vowel. 3.